template.name: Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool
template.description: This template used for Supermicro X9DRL monitoring via ipmitool. Tested on Debian Linux 10

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.3dot3v,#3)>3.936 or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.3dot3v,#3)<2.928
trigger.name: 3.3V Critical with value [{ITEM.VALUE}]V

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.5v,#3)>6.912 or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.5v,#3)<4.480
trigger.name: 5V Critical with value [{ITEM.VALUE}]V

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.12v,#3)>13.250 or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.12v,#3)<10.812
trigger.name: 12V Critical with value [{ITEM.VALUE}]V

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.cpu1.temp,#3)>{$CPU_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: CPU1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.cpu2.temp,#3)>{$CPU_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: CPU2 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.dimm.p1.a1.temp,#3)>{$DIMM_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: P1-DIMMA1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.dimm.p1.b1.temp,#3)>{$DIMM_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: P1-DIMMB1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.dimm.p1.c1.temp,#3)>{$DIMM_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: P1-DIMMC1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.dimm.p1.d1.temp,#3)>{$DIMM_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: P1-DIMMD1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.dimm.p2.e1.temp,#3)>{$DIMM_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: P2-DIMME1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.dimm.p2.f1.temp,#3)>{$DIMM_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: P2-DIMMF1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.dimm.p2.g1.temp,#3)>{$DIMM_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: P2-DIMMG1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.dimm.p2.h1.temp,#3)>{$DIMM_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: P2-DIMMH1 Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan1,#3)<{$FAN_RPM_LOW} or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan1,#3)>{$FAN_RPM_HIGH}
trigger.name: FAN1 Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}] RPM

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan2,#3)<{$FAN_RPM_LOW} or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan2,#3)>{$FAN_RPM_HIGH}
trigger.name: FAN2 Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}] RPM

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan3,#3)<{$FAN_RPM_LOW} or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan3,#3)>{$FAN_RPM_HIGH}
trigger.name: FAN3 Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}] RPM

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan4,#3)<{$FAN_RPM_LOW} or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan4,#3)>{$FAN_RPM_HIGH}
trigger.name: FAN4 Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}] RPM

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan5,#3)<{$FAN_RPM_LOW} or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan5,#3)>{$FAN_RPM_HIGH}
trigger.name: FAN5 Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}] RPM

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan6,#3)<{$FAN_RPM_LOW} or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fan6,#3)>{$FAN_RPM_HIGH}
trigger.name: FAN6 Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}] RPM

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fana,#3)<{$FAN_RPM_LOW} or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fana,#3)>{$FAN_RPM_HIGH}
trigger.name: FANA Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}] RPM

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fanb,#3)<{$FAN_RPM_LOW} or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.fanb,#3)>{$FAN_RPM_HIGH}
trigger.name: FANB Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}] RPM

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.pch.temp,#3)>{$SYS_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: PCH Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.peripheral.temp,#3)>{$SYS_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: Peripheral Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.plus.1dot5v,#3)<1.344 or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.plus.1dot5v,#3)>1.648
trigger.name: +1.5V Critical with value [{ITEM.VALUE}]V

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.plus.3dot3vsb,#3)<2.928 or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.plus.3dot3vsb,#3)>3.648
trigger.name: +3.3VSB Critical with value [{ITEM.VALUE}]V

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.plus.5vsb,#3)<4.480 or last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.plus.5vsb,#3)>5.504
trigger.name: +5VSB Critical with value [{ITEM.VALUE}]V

trigger.expression: last(/Supermicro X9DRL-3F via ipmitool/ipmitool.system.temp,#3)>{$SYS_TEMP_CRIT}
trigger.name: System Temp Critical [{ITEM.VALUE}]
